quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  42,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  42,1,h m
  42,2,a seen q
  42,3,isi terhan Allah ghalib o hakeem tumhari taraf aur tum se pehlay guzray hue ( Rasolo-n ) ki taraf wahi karta raha hai
  42,4,"asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch bhi hai usi ka hai, woh bartar aur azeem hai"
  42,5,"qareeb hai ke aasman oopar se phatt parrin farishtay apne rab ki hamd ke sath uss ki tasbeeh kar rahay hain aur zameen walon ke haq mein dar guzar ki darkhwasten kiye jatay hain aagah raho, haqeeqat mein Allah ghafoor o Raheem hi hai"
  42,6,"jin logon ne uss ko chore kar apne kuch dosray sarparast bana rakhay hain, Allah hi unn par nigaran hai, tum un ke hawala daar nahi ho"
  42,7,"haan, isi terhan ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh quran arabi hum ne tumhari taraf wahi kya hai taakay tum bustiyon ke markaz ( shehar mecca ) aur uss ke gird o paish rehne walon ko khabardaar kar do, aur jama honay ke din se dara do jin ke anay mein koi shak nahi aik giroh ko jannat mein jana hai aur dosray giroh ko dozakh mein"
  42,8,"agar Allah chahta to inn sab ko aik hi ummat bana deta, magar woh jisay chahta hai apni rehmat mein daakhil karta hai, aur zaalmon ka nah koi walii hai nah madad gaar"
  42,9,"kya yeh ( aisay nadaan hain ke ) unhon ne ussay chore kar dosray walii bana rakhay hain? walii to Allah hi hai, wohi mُrdon ko zindah karta hai, aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai"
  42,10,"tumahray darmain jis maamla mein bhi ikhtilaaf ho, uss ka faisla karna Allah ka kaam hai wohi Allah mera rab hai, usi par mein ne bharosa kya, aur usi ki taraf mein rujoo karta hon"
  42,11,"asmano aur zameen ka bananay wala, jis ne tumhari apni jins se tumahray liye jore peda kiye, aur isi terhan janwaron mein bhi ( aُnhi ke hum jins ) jore banaye, aur iss tareeqa se woh tumhari naslen phelata hai kaayenaat ki koi cheez is ke mushaba nahi, woh sab kuch suneney aur dekhnay wala hai"
  42,12,"asmano aur zameen ke khazanon ki knjyan usi ke paas hain, jisay chahta hai khula rizaq deta hai aur jisay chahta hai npa tala deta hai, ussay har cheez ka ilm hai"
  42,13,"uss ne tumahray liye deen ka wohi tareeqa muqarrar kya hai jis ka hukum uss ne Nooh ko diya tha, aur jisay ( aeMuhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) ab tumhari taraf hum ne wahi ke zareya se bheja hai, aur jis ki hadaayat hum ibrahim aur moose aur eesa ko day chuke hain, iss takeed ke sath ke qaim karo iss deen ko aur uss mein mutafarraq nah ho jao yahi baat inn mushriqeen ko sakht nagawaar hui hai jis ki taraf aeMuhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamtum inhen dawat day rahay ho Allah jisay chahta hai apna kar laita hai, aur woh apni taraf anay ka rasta usi ko dekhata hai jo uss ki taraf rujoo kere"
  42,14,"logon mein jo tafarruqa ro numa howa woh iss ke baad howa ke unn ke paas ilm aa chuka tha, aur is bana par howa ke woh aapas mein aik dosray par zayad-ti karna chahtay thay agar tera rab pehlay hi yeh nah farma chuka hota ke aik waqt muqarrar taq faisla multawi rakha jaye ga to un ka qazia chuka diya gaya hota aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke uglo ke baad jo log kitaab ke waris banaye gay woh uss ki taraf se barray iztiraab angaiz shak mein parre hue hain"
  42,15,"chunkay yeh haalat peda ho chuki hai is liye ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, ab tum usi deen ki taraf dawat do, aur jis terhan tumhe hukum diya gaya hai uss par mazbooti ke sath qaim ho jao, aur inn logo n ki khwahisaat ka itebaa nah karo, aur inn se keh do ke :"" Allah ne jo kitaab bhi nazil ki hai mein uss par imaan laya mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke mein tumahray darmain insaaf karoon Allah hi hamara rab bhi hai aur tumhara rab bhi hamaray aamaal hamaray liye hain aur tumahray aamaal tumahray liye hamaray aur tumahray darmain koi jhagra nahi Allah aik roz hum sab ko jama kere ga aur usi ki taraf sab ko jana hai """
  42,16,"Allah ki dawat par labaik kahe jaane ke baad jo log ( labaik kehnay walon se ) Allah ke deen ke maamla mein jhagrre karte hain, unn ki Hujjat baazi unn ke rab ke nazdeek baatil hai, aur unn par is ka ghazab hai aur unn ke liye sakht azaab hai"
  42,17,"woh Allah hi hai jis ne haq ke sath yeh kitaab aur maizaan nazil ki hai aur tumhe kya khabar, shayad ke faislay ki gharri qareeb hi aa lagi ho"
  42,18,"jo log is ke anay par imaan nahi rakhtay woh to is ke liye jaldi machate hain, magar jo is par imaan rakhtay hain woh is se drtay hain aur jantay hain ke yaqeenan woh anay wali hai khoob sun lau, jo log uss gharri ke anay mein shak daalnay wali bhsin karte hain woh gumraahi mein bohat daur nikal gay hain"
  42,19,"Allah apne bundon par bohat meharban hai jisay jo kuch chahta hai deta hai, woh barri qowat wala aur zabardast hai"
  42,20,"jo koi akhirat ki khaiti chahta hai uss ki khaiti ko hum berhate hain, aur jo duniya ki khaiti chahta hai ussay duniya hi mein se dete hain magar akhirat mein uss ka koi hissa nahi hai"
  42,21,kya yeh log kuch aisay shareek khuda rakhtay hain jinhon ne inn ke liye deen ki noiyat rakhnay wala aik aisa tareeqa muqarrar kar diya hai jis ka Allah ne azan nahi diya? agar faislay ki baat pehlay tey nah ho gayi hoti to un ka qazia chuka diya gaya hota yaqeenan inn zaalmon ke liye dard naak azaab hai
  42,22,"tum dekho ge ke yeh zalim uss waqt apne kiye ke injaam se dar rahay hon ge aur woh inn par aa kar rahay ga bakhilaf iss ke jo log imaan le aeye hain aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye hain woh jannat ke gulistanon mein hon ge, jo kuch bhi woh chahain ge apne rab ke haan payen ge, yahi bara fazl hai"
  42,23,"yeh hai woh cheez jis ki khush khaberi Allah apne unn bundon ko deta hai jinhon ne maan liya aur naik amal kiye ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn logon se keh do ke mein iss kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon, Albata qaraabat ki mohabbat zaroor chahta hon jo koi bhalai kamaye ga hum is ke liye is bhalai mein khoobi ka izafah kar den ge be shak Allah bara Dur guzar karne wala aur qader daan hai"
  42,24,kya yeh log kehte hain ke iss shakhs ne Allah par jhoota bohtan ghurr liya hai? agar Allah chahay to tumahray dil par mohar kar day woh baatil ko mita deta hai aur haq ko apne farmanon se haq kar dekhata hai woh seenon ke chupay hue raaz jaanta hai
  42,25,"wohi hai jo apne bundon se tauba qubool karta hai aur buraiyon se dar guzar karta hai, halaank tum logon ke sab af-aal ka aُ se ilm hai"
  42,26,"woh imaan laane walon aur naik amal karne walon ki dua qubool karta hai aur apne fazl se un ko aur ziyada deta hai rahay inkaar karne walay, to un ke liye dard naak saza hai"
  42,27,"agar Allah apne sab bundon ko khula rizaq day deta to woh zameen mein sar kashi ka tufaan barpaa kar dete, magar woh aik hisaab se jitna chahta hai nazil karta hai, yaqeenan woh apne bundon se ba khabar hai aur unn par nigah rakhta hai"
  42,28,"wohi hai jo logon ke mayoos ho jaane ke baad meen brsata hai aur apni rehmat phela deta hai, aur wohi qabil tareef walii hai"
  42,29,"uss ki nshanyon mein se hai yeh zameen aur asmano ki paidaiesh, aur yeh jandaar makhloqaat jo uss ne dono jagah phela rakhi hain woh jab chahay inhen akhatta kar sakta hai"
  42,30,"tum par jo museebat bhi aayi hai, tumahray apne hathon ki kamaai se aayi hai, aur bohat seKasoroo-n se woh waisay hi Dur guzar kar jata hai"
  42,31,"tum zameen mein apne khuda ko aajiz kar dainay walay nahi ho, aur Allah ke muqablay mein tum koi haami o nasir nahi rakhtay"
  42,32,uss ki nshanyon mein se hain yeh jahaaz jo samandar mein pahoron ki terhan nazar atay hain
  42,33,Allah jab chahay howa ko saakin kar day aur yeh samandar ki peeth par kharray ke kharray reh jayen iss mein barri nishanain hain har uss shakhs ke liye jo kamaal darja sabr o shukar karne wala ho
  42,34,ya ( unn par sawaar honay walon ke ) bohat se gunaaho se Dur guzar karte hue un ke chand hi krtoton ki Padaash mein inhen duubo day
  42,35,aur uss waqt hamari ayaat mein jhagrre karne walon ko pata chal jaye ke un ke liye koi jaye panah nahi hai
  42,36,"jo kuch bhi tum logon ko diya gaya hai woh mehez duniya ki chand roza zindagi ka sir o samaan hai, aur jo kuch Allah ke haan hai woh behtar bhi hai aur paidaar bhi woh unn logon ke liye hai jo imaan laaye hain aur apne rab par bharosa karte hain"
  42,37,jo barray barray gunaaho aur be hiyai ke kamon se parhaiz karte hain aur agar gussa aa jaye to dar guzar kar ja te hain
  42,38,"jo apne rab ka hukum mantay hain, namaz qaim karte hain, apne mamlaat aapas ke mashwaray se chillate hain, hum ne jo kuch bhi rizaq inhen diya hai uss mein se kharch karte hain"
  42,39,aur jab un par zayad-ti ki jati hai to is ka muqaabla karte hain
  42,40,"buraiee ka badla waisi hi buraiee hai, phir jo koi maaf kar day aur islaah kere uss ka ajar Allah ke zimma hai, Allah zaalmon ko pasand nahi karta"
  42,41,aur jo log zulm honay ke baad badla len unn ko malamat nahi ki ja sakti
  42,42,malamat ke mustahiq to woh hain jo dosaron par zulm karte hain aur zameen mein na-haq zyadtyan karte hain aisay logon ke liye dard naak azaab hai
  42,43,"Albata jo shakhs sabr se kaam le aur dar guzar kere, to yeh barri awallulazmai ke kamon mein se hai"
  42,44,jis ko Allah hi gumraahi mein pheink day uss ka koi snbhalne wala Allah ke baad nahi hai tum dekho ge ke yeh zalim jab azaab dekhen ge to kahin ge ab palatnay ki bhi koi Sabeel hai ?
  42,45,"aur tum dekho ge ke yeh jahannum ke samnay jab laaye jayen ge to zillat ke maaray jhuke ja rahay hon ge aur uss ko nazar bacha bacha kar kanankhyonse dekhen ge uss waqt woh log jo imaan laaye thay kahin ge ke waqai asal zayan car wohi hain jinhon ne aaj qayamat ke din apne aap ko aur apne mut'alaqeen ko khasaray mein daal diya khabardaar raho, zalim log mustaqil azaab mein hon ge"
  42,46,aur un ke koi haami o sarparast nah hon ge jo Allah ke muqablay mein un ki madad ko ayen jisay Allah gumraahi mein pheink day is ke liye bachao ki koi Sabeel nahi
  42,47,maan lau apne rab ki baat qabal is ke ke woh din aeye jis ke talnay ki koi soorat Allah ki taraf se nahi hai uss din tumahray liye koi jaye panah nah hogi aur nah koi tumahray haal ko badalny ki koshish karne wala ho ga
  42,48,"ab agar yeh log mun morty hain to ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tum ko un par nigehbaan bana kar to nahi bheja hai tum par to sirf baat pouncha dainay ki zimma daari hai ensaan ka haal yeh hai ke jab hum usay apni rehmat ka maza chukhatayhain to uss par phool jata hai, aur agar is ke apne hathon ka kya dhara kisi museebat ki shakal mein uss par ulat parta hai to sakht nashukara ban jata hai"
  42,49,"Allah zameen aur asmano ki badshahi ka maalik hai, jo kuch chahta hai peda karta hai, jisay chahta hai larkiyan deta hai, jisay chahta hai larke deta hai"
  42,50,"jisay chahta hai larke aur larkiyan mila jala kar deta hai, aur jisay chahta hai banjh kar deta hai woh sab kuch jaanta aur har cheez par Qadir hai"
  42,51,"kisi bashar ka yeh maqam nahi hai ke Allah uss se rubaroo baat kere uss ki baat ya to wahi ( isharay ) ke tor par hoti hai, ya parday ke peechay se, ya phir woh koi pegham Bar ( farishta ) bhejta hai aur woh uss ke hukum se jo kuch woh chahta hai, wahi karta hai, woh bartar aur hakeem hai"
  42,52,"aur isi terhan ( aeMuhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) hum ne apne hukum se aik rooh tumhari taraf wahi ki hai tumhe kuch pata nah tha ke kitaab kya hoti hai aur imaan kya hota hai, magar uss rooh ko hum ne aik roshni bana diya jis se hum raah dikhata hain apne bundon mein se jisay chahtay hain yaqeenan tum seedhay rastay ki taraf rahnumai kar rahay ho"
  42,53,"uss khuda ke rastay ki taraf jo zameen aur asmano ki har cheez ka maalik hai khabardaar raho, saaray mamlaat Allah hi ki taraf rujoo karte hain"
